******************************
**** Database Integration ****
******************************
https://expressjs.com/en/guide/database-integration.html

This link are the various db options available to use through Express.
Working with them is all the same: you install a driver for the db type you want to use, then you get a module with a simple API.


In the case of MongoDB specifically	there is another package called "Mongoose" which is built on top of the MongoClient.
Instead of using MongoClient driver directly, we use Mongoose because it gives a simpler API.
